{
  "name": "hometool 地理編碼",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## hometool 地理編碼\n\n每 5 分鐘處理一批 75 個地址（程式內部以 1.1s 間隔遵守 Nominatim 1 req/s 政策；單批最壞約 4.4 分鐘，再大會跟下一批重疊）。\n回應的 `remaining` = 還沒補座標的交易筆數，追平後每次執行會秒回、不做事。\n\n### 首次設定\nHTTP 節點掛上與「實價登錄匯入」**同一個** Header Auth 憑證。\n\n單批失敗不重試——下一批 5 分鐘後自然接手。",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 360
      },
      "id": "note-1",
      "name": "說明",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-560, -160]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "minutes",
              "minutesInterval": 5
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "schedule-trigger",
      "name": "每 5 分鐘",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [-140, -140]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "manual-trigger",
      "name": "手動執行",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-140, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://hometool.zeabur.app/api/admin/geocode?limit=75",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 290000
        }
      },
      "id": "http-geocode",
      "name": "地理編碼一批",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [120, -40]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "每 5 分鐘": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "地理編碼一批",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "手動執行": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "地理編碼一批",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
